description: Gets a list of labeling jobs assigned to a specified work team.

parameters.name: WorkteamArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the work team for which you want to see labeling jobs for.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobSummaryList
nested_items.description: An array of LabelingJobSummary objects, each describing a labeling job.

nested_items.name: LabelingJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the labeling job that the work team is assigned to.

nested_items.name: JobReferenceCode
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for a labeling job. You can use this to refer to a specific labeling job.

nested_items.name: WorkRequesterAccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the account used to start the labeling job.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the labeling job was created.

nested_items.name: LabelCounters
nested_items.description: Provides information about the progress of a labeling job.

nested_items.name: HumanLabeled
nested_items.description: The total number of data objects labeled by a human worker.

nested_items.name: PendingHuman
nested_items.description: The total number of data objects that need to be labeled by a human worker.

nested_items.name: Total
nested_items.description: The total number of tasks in the labeling job.

nested_items.name: NumberOfHumanWorkersPerDataObject
nested_items.description: The configured number of workers per data object.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, SageMaker returns this token. To retrieve the next set of labeling jobs, use it in the subsequent request.
